image,4164,200,IMG_5949.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,4164,200,IMG_5973.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,4164,200,IMG_5968.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,4164,200,IMG_5979.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,4164,200,IMG_5988.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><br /></span></span></p>','Зимовий відпочинок дітей парафії','uk',2681,4164,0,'Любов Михайлюк'),
